Efe tried again and again to achieve the document signed during the VIth Ordinary Meeting of the leaders of States and of government of Unasur, but the ministry of Foreign Affairs and the presidency signalled at first that it would be disclosed after the fence of the summit, then maintained that it would be published from instant to the other one on the Internet site of the Peruvian government.
When they were questioned about the text, they signalled that its contents had been displayed by the president of Peru, Ollante Humala, during short statements to the press.
The access of the journalists to information concerning the summit was always limited.
During day, only the video without the sound of the presidential assembly with the message "audio, private session restrained" was broadcast in the press-room.
Not enough information which circulated between the journalists those was given by the press attachés of some of the governments of Unasur which attended appointment, except for the Peruvian spokesperson.
